nt|^z@3^b@2|at|^^^^|fp|t-title|at|More on  Degree of Control|fp||at|^^^^|
cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  So a holding of Ax is said to have 1st and 3rd round control of the suit, 1st round control because of the Ace and 3rd round control because partner can ruff the 3rd round of the suit.

