cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  "Crafting" Asking Bid sequences is a skill you will acquire only gradually.

Even then, you will not get it "right" 100% of the time (I certainly don't).

It's also important to realise when you need to STOP Asking, because you cannot afford one of the possible responses.

If any of the possible responses to an ask would take you beyond the safe level, then you cannot afford to ask (but you might KNOW that the more expensive responses to, for example, an Epsilon Ask, are NOT possible, because all of Responder's controls are accounted for)

